{"tid":1514954,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「警世」而家犯法係唔會有事，快突破第一層心理關口","createTime":"2019-08-29T03:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T07:43:11.000Z","uid":89974,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb700223013db987779a69c515d3119d2a8aab4","tid":1514954,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:05:59.000Z","msg":"想同個班仲潔身自愛連閘都唔敢跳既人講：<br />\n<br />\n只要我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">贏咗</span></span>，係乜事都唔會有，例如暴動罪<br />\n就算未贏，只要你條罪唔大，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人夠多</span></span>都係唔會入到你，例如跳閘<br />\n<br />\n當然我唔係叫你而家去打劫金行，呢啲係會有事的，唔該用番良知去諗野<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再拘泥於佢用咩罪告你，咩街坊送頭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家警權就係大到點都搵到條罪charge你，打鳩你，我地先要企出嚟反對阿嘛</span></span><br />\n暴動？非法集結？藏有攻擊性武器？只要贏到你仲駛乜驚佢用咩嚟搞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正要避免既係<span style=\"color: red;\">不可復原永久性損傷</span>，例如眼，腳，骨，呢啲無得100%復原既位係真正既損耗。至於留唔留案底？驚乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再者，你再潔身自愛，<span style=\"color: red;\">輸咗你都係等俾人告嫁咋<br />\n</span>，今次輸咗23條過硬，仲記唔記得黨報成日話我地港獨啊？到時大家全部入哂分裂國家罪係集中營見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一個有良知既人，唔會因爲在必要時期犯法就會無止境地成為罪犯<br />\n<br />\n一個無良知既人，就算有哂規例都會搵盡方法去鑽圈子</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  For TLDR<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持同樣立場既人，打擊敵方立場既人<br />\n而唔係屌尻自己人，同敵人講道理日</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c7de52ea29c5fe7dd7f73332219de56a475b5d8","tid":1514954,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTykUks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTykUks.jpg&h=e262c427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3J6Zqr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3J6Zqr9.jpg&h=398279dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFi3Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFi3Tp.jpg&h=1a5d1359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">901 和你塞 13:00 見</span></span> <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=4c846ccd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=e7d59af9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=18fd692c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=dcfad6bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102458676557543%2Fposts%2F1582783125191750%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=fc5ab30e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo</a><br />\n將窗嗌口號變成一種普及的生活方式，會好大感染力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyn9vh9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcyn9vh9.png&h=f1d434e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3640318c421870254e27235fd2f35d6098cab6d","tid":1514954,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2276781de9cd21111699cd28a4c3a88388edd0af","tid":1514954,"uid":307114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"其實好多時係驚仆街多啲<br />\n毒撚平時唔做運動ga ma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9cb308370c1340fd796db6daadd58c8616c846","tid":1514954,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d00a9907bf89b232e2e409778505a355fa17932","tid":1514954,"uid":89974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{