ces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再拖落去就等有後生仔俾人斬死"},{"pid":"a53504967618763e736ddd50ffb846123f0edf11","tid":1514954,"uid":267738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:43:11.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幫幫手簽petition</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-hong-kong-51st-state?fbclid=IwAR0uVBhdGFxFjGNbmXTqFi2NPQf85-RP9BrP2Z6bjEBJ8iDZqVWL3i1Mvag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fmake-hong-kong-51st-state%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0uVBhdGFxFjGNbmXTqFi2NPQf85-RP9BrP2Z6bjEBJ8iDZqVWL3i1Mvag&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=8aaf0c27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-hong-kong-51st-state?fbclid=IwAR0uVBhdGFxFjGNbmXTqFi2NPQf85-RP9BrP2Z6bjEBJ8iDZqVWL3i1Mvag</a>"}]}